The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Bengal | Cop killed
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         Cop killed
                            
	Calcutta, Oct. 24: A 45-year-old highway inspector, attached to the Howrah traffic police, was crushed to death by a speeding truck on Kona Expressway around 10 tonight.        
	Police said Haribishnu Chakraborty, on patrol duty, was on a bike when the truck hit him. He died on the spot.                                                                                                                                                                         
